   <summary>Improves Magento support for Varnish caching and generates 2.1 and 3.0 compatible VCLs.</summary>
   <description>Turpentine is a Magento extension to improve Magento&apos;s compatibility with Varnish, a very-fast caching reverse-proxy. By default, Varnish doesn&apos;t cache requests with cookies and Magento sends the frontend cookie with every request causing a (near) zero hit-rate for Varnish&apos;s cache. Turpentine provides Varnish configuration files (VCLs) to work with Magento and modifies Magento&apos;s behaviour to significantly improve the cache hit rate.</description>
